{"tid":1075830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有牽繩就能進店　美夫婦帶700公斤巨牛踢館","createTime":"2019-03-24T12:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T14:02:10.000Z","uid":32511,"like":722,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":109,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8253baca913791bef313df7f1ed3c8bd1f479c","tid":1075830,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:08:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xWfURYsgwfQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxWfURYsgwfQ&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8uBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=e7c9d148\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xWfURYsgwfQ</a><br />\n<br />\n美國德州休士頓一對夫婦為了測試寵物店的口號「歡迎帶寵物進店」是不是真的，周一（18日）把一頭重達726公斤的非洲長角牛（African Watusi）帶進店，結果這頭牛獲得店員們的熱烈歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n布朗寧（Vincent Browning）和謝利（Shelly Browning）近日看到當地剛開幕的連鎖寵物店「Petco」打出：「只要有牽繩，歡迎飼主帶寵物進來逛」的口號後，決定測試業者的宣傳是不是「虛張聲勢」。兩人周一帶著套上項圈的「寵物」奧利弗（Oliver）上門，本以為會被阻擋，沒想到工作人員見到奧利弗後，反而熱情接待。<br />\n<br />\n布朗寧表示，奧利弗的體型龐大，且可能會在店內亂大便，但當他們來到店門口時，不但沒有被阻擋，還被熱情地請進店。「Petco的員工們真的很棒，不但張開雙臂歡迎我們，而且態度非常友好、有禮貌，這間Petco門市是我目前為止最喜歡的」。他又說，當奧利弗順利進到店內後，店員們紛紛搶著跟牠合照，而當天的影片在臉書公開後，也一夕爆紅。「我從來沒想到結果會這樣，真的很謝謝大家。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LQhCE5O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLQhCE5O.jpg&h=6792c0d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FgXCE5O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFgXCE5O.jpg&h=06101ebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LeFgVD9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLeFgVD9.jpg&h=2669c6b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pEH3AD9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpEH3AD9.jpg&h=f010bff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/96a1nja.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F96a1nja.jpg&h=b79316b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3P1zHja.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3P1zHja.jpg&h=40e37e91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28cb5a07658609b5b2b674423590cafbe33defa8","tid":1075830,"uid":113000,"like":1186,"dislike":4,"score":1182,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:11:40.000Z","msg":"隻牛對角好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac146dbe08709335a76f0cc4f7e25a490e6a9089","tid":1075830,"uid":206895,"like":35,"dislike":190,"score":-155,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:12:30.000Z","msg":"隻牛角應該好值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d7774aad32a22cacd771eef6f6fcd4c12556fc","tid":1075830,"uid":155818,"like":247,"dislike":3,"score":244,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:13:03.000Z","msg":"對角好撚柒型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038efac688dba80565722a03d8acdafe9c2c4892","tid":1075830,"uid":51469,"like":586,"dislike":4,"score":582,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:13:52.000Z","msg":"對角大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/97973/transform/20160731/Q-FA-fxunyya2891513.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2F97973%2Ftransform%2F20160731%2FQ-FA-fxunyya2891513.jpg&h=fee0b1f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f3e17c504b69accab193bd8af9913fef98ba3d3","tid":1075830,"uid":52122,"like":197,"dislike":1,"score":196,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:14:30.000Z","msg":"嘩屌對角好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592152dc6154212995045cb20c6e29348c586246","tid":1075830,"uid":133519,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:15:56.000Z","msg":"插撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgm